#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Basics:</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Det grundlæggende:</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Do you want to go further?</strong></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Vil du tage det et skridt "
"videre?</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Use case:</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Brugsscenarie:</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>1. Flow 1:</strong> Most products need a human assessment as the "
"remaining quantity cannot be automatically computed. For those, a Recurring "
"Task is created in the Project App. This task reappears every week, and you "
"can personalize it with a checklist to avoid forgetting anything."
msgstr ""
"<strong>1. Flow 1:</strong> De fleste produkter kræver en manuel vurdering, "
"da den resterende mængde ikke kan beregnes automatisk. For disse oprettes en "
"tilbagevendende opgave i Projektappen. Opgaven vises hver uge, og du kan "
"tilpasse den med en tjekliste, så intet bliver glemt."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>2. Flow 2:</strong> For products that can be tracked, such as "
"bottled beers and sodas, you can use automated purchases. To try it, "
"navigate to your Point of Sale and sell a Blond Beer to a customer."
msgstr ""
"<strong>2. Flow 2:</strong> For produkter, der kan spores, såsom flaskeøl og "
"sodavand, kan du bruge automatiske indkøb. For at prøve det kan du gå til "
"dit kassesystem og sælge en lys øl til en kunde."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Bar</span></strong><br/>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Bar</span></strong><br/>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Website</font></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders "
"directly in Odoo or go live with your \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-shop</"
"font></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"En gratis, skræddersyet og integreret <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"hjemmeside</font></strong> med kun få klik. Begynd at modtage ordrer direkte "
"i Odoo, eller få din \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">e-butik</font>"
"</strong> online på få minutter."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_31_product_template
msgid "Aperol"
msgstr "Aperol"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As an administrator your pin is 3333. You can edit the pin of your employees "
"in the Employee App, in the Settings tab."
msgstr ""
"Som administrator er din PIN-kode 3333. Du kan ændre dine medarbejderes PIN-"
"koder i medarbejderappen under fanen \"Indstillinger\"."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At the end of your service, remember to close your register. To do so, in "
"the Point of Sale App, select \"Close Register\" in the top-right menu. You "
"can then precise your cash amount and validate the closing."
msgstr ""
"Husk at lukke kassebogen, når du er færdig med din service. Vælg "
"\"Luk kasse\" i menuen øverst til højre i POS-appen. Herefter kan du "
"indtaste kassebeløbet og bekræfte afslutningen."

