#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "By doing so, you have only 23 beers left in your stock."
msgstr "Det betyder, at du kun har 23 øl tilbage på lager."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By the way, you can see another project with recurring tasks. This one is a "
"demo for cleaning tasks."
msgstr ""
"Du kan desuden se et andet projekt med tilbagevendende opgaver. Dette er en "
"demo af rengøringsopgaver."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products."
msgstr ""
"Når du har uploadet demodataene til dette modul, er din database blevet "
"fyldt med nogle produkter."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.project,name:bar_industry.project_project_2
msgid "Cleaning"
msgstr "Rengøring"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Få mere at vide om Odoo i vores"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Få indsigt i de grundlæggende funktioner i denne pakke, og udforsk de mange "
"muligheder, Odoo tilbyder, for at optimere din oplevelse."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "Vil du tage det et skridt videre?"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Don't forget to hit the \"Order\" button each time you change an order. This "
"will forward the order to the Kitchen Display."
msgstr ""
"Husk at klikke på knappen \"Bestil\", hver gang du ændrer en ordre. Så "
"sendes ordren videre til køkkenskærmen."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.task.type,name:bar_industry.project_task_type_2
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Udført"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:hr.department,name:bar_industry.hr_department_2
msgid "Employees"
msgstr "Medarbejdere"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "From the Point of Sale, open your register on the main dashboard."
msgstr "Åbn kassen fra hoveddashboardet i POS-appen."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_3_product_template
msgid "Gift Card"
msgstr "Gavekort"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to your Purchase App to easily create Requests for Proposal or Purchase "
"Orders."
msgstr ""
"Gå til Indkøbsappen for hurtigt at oprette tilbudsanmodninger eller ordrer."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_29_product_template
msgid "Green lemon"
msgstr "Lime"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.pricelist,name:bar_industry.product_pricelist_2
msgid "Happy Hour"
msgstr "Happy Hour"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "Hej!"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_30_product_template
msgid "Ice cubes"
msgstr "Isterninger"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your Purchase App, you can see a new Purchase Order that "
"is ready to be sent. You can choose a packaging if your product has an "
"existing one."
msgstr ""
"Når du åbner Indkøbsappen, vil du se en ny ordre, der er klar til "
"afsendelse. Du kan vælge en emballage, hvis der allerede findes en til dit "
"produkt."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to assign them an Odoo user account, you can select a related "
"user in the \"HR Settings\" tab."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil tildele dem en Odoo-brugerkonto, kan du vælge en passende bruger "
"under fanen \"HR-indstillinger\"."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Demo - Use Case (In the next Knowledge Article)."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil gennemgå en praktisk rundvisning af dette modul, bør du "
"importere demodata og afprøve demoens brugsscenarie (som beskrevet i næste "
"artikel i Vidensdelingsappen)."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_27_product_template
msgid "Lemon"
msgstr "Citron"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>, \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media "
"Marketing</font></strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS "
"Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Administrér alle dine kommunikationskanaler ét sted med Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Automatiseret marketing</font></strong>, "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-mailmarketing</font></strong>,\n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Markedsføring "
"på sociale medier</font></strong> og <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\""
">SMS-marketing</font></strong>."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Håndter din bogføring nemmere end nogensinde i et fuldt integreret miljø. "
"(<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Bogføringsapp</font></strong>)"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_28_product_template
msgid "Mint"
msgstr "Mynte"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into "
"an additional cashier (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er fuldt integreret i én app. Download den, og forvandl din telefon til "
"et værktøj, hvormed du kan bruge din telefon som et ekstra kasseapparat "
"(m.m.)."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo giver dig ubegrænsede muligheder, såsom:"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Oversigten viser naturligvis kun de funktioner, der følger med pakken. Du "
"kan tilføje nye apps, redigere eller slette demodata og prøve dig frem!"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"Receipt\" smart button to "
"validate your receipt and add these new products to your stock."
msgstr ""
"Så snart produkterne er ankommet, kan du klikke på knappen "
"\"Varemodtagelse\" for at bekræfte modtagelsen og tilføje de nye produkter "
"til dit lager."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your customers easily with the<strong> "
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Planlæg dine arrangementer, og kontakt dine kunder via <strong> <font class="
"\"text-o-color-1\">Arrangementerappen</font></strong>."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Plan your services easily using the Planning App."
msgstr "Nem planlægning af dine vagter med Planlægningsappen."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Kontakt os"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are displayed in the smart buttons on top of your product. "
"You can see a minimum quantity, and a maximum. Each time the forecast stock "
"lowers beneath the minimum stock, it automatically creates a purchase order "
"to replenish to the maximum quantity."
msgstr ""
"Reglerne for genbestilling vises i de intelligente knapper øverst på dit "
"produkt. Du kan se både minimums- og maksimumsmængder. Hver gang den "
"forventede lagerbeholdning falder under minimum, oprettes der automatisk en "
"genopfyldningsordre op til maksimale mængde."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Replenishment is essential but challenging for a bar owner to systematize."
msgstr ""
"Genopfyldning er uundværlig for ejeren af en bar, men kan være svær at sætte "
"i system."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:planning.role,name:bar_industry.planning_role_1
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Service"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.project,name:bar_industry.project_project_1
msgid "Suppliers Orders"
msgstr "Leverandørordrer"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:bar_industry.project_project_1
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:bar_industry.project_project_2
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "Opgaver"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kitchen Display</font></strong> "
"will ensure a great follow up of every order in your bar and kitchen."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Køkkenskærmen</font></strong> sikrer "
"en effektiv opfølgning på alle bestillinger i din bar og dit køkken."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The current setup requires your employees to pin to log in the POS register. "
"This helps you manage rights and accesses."
msgstr ""
"Den nuværende konfiguration kræver, at dine medarbejdere logger ind for at "
"få adgang til kassesystemet. Dette gør det nemmere at administrere "
"rettigheder og adgang."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The stock is only updated when you close your register. Let's do it before "
"continuing to the next step."
msgstr ""
"Lagerbeholdningen opdateres først, når kassen lukkes. Lad os gøre dette, "
"inden vi fortsætter til næste trin."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"De er alle inkluderet i dit nuværende abonnement. Gå straks på opdagelse i "
"dem! 🙃"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:pos.category,name:bar_industry.pos_category_4
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Drikkepenge"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:project.task.type,name:bar_industry.project_task_type_1
msgid "To Do"
msgstr "Gøremål"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use case:"
msgstr "Brugsscenarie:"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory App</font></strong> "
"to manage your stock and receive products."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Lagerappen</font></strong> til "
"at administrere dit lager og modtage produkter."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning App</font></strong> "
"to schedule your shifts and share it with your employees."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planlægningsappen</font></"
"strong> til at planlægge vagter og dele dem med dine medarbejdere."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale</font></strong> "
"for your sales at the desk. You can also download the Odoo Mobile App on any "
"phone to take orders."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">POS</font></strong> til dine "
"salg ved kassen. Du kan også downloade Odoos Mobile App på en hvilken som "
"helst telefon for at registrere ordrer."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project App</font></strong> "
"to never miss a reordering or a cleaning task."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Projektappen</font></strong>, så "
"du aldrig går glip af en genbestillings- eller rengøringsopgave."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App</font></strong> "
"to reorder your products."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Indkøbsappen</font></strong> til "
"at genbestille dine produkter."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:bar_industry.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Velkommen! God fornøjelse med at gå på opdagelse."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily edit the floor map by clicking \"Edit plan\" in the top-right "
"menu when on the table selection of your Point of Sale."
msgstr ""
"Du kan nemt redigere plantegningen ved at klikke på \"Redigér plantegning\" "
"øverst til højre i bordoversigten i kassesystemet."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now email your Request for Proposal to your vendor or confirm it "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Du kan nu sende din tilbudsanmodning til leverandøren via e-mail eller "
"bekræfte den manuelt."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that there is a reordering rule configured for this product if "
"you go to Inventory  &amp;gt; Products  &amp;gt; Blond Beer"
msgstr ""
"Du kan se, at der er oprettet en genbestillingsregel for dette produkt, når "
"du går til Lager  &amp;gt; Produkter  &amp;gt; Lys øl"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har nu gennemført demoens brugsscenarie. Odoo kan tilpasses på utallige "
"måder, så løsningen matcher netop din virksomheds behov."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You currently have two steps in your Kitchen Display: one for the kitchen/"
"bar and one for the service. You can configure steps in the kitchen display "
"configuration menu."
msgstr ""
"Du har i øjeblikket to trin på din køkkenskærm: et til køkkenet/baren og et "
"til serveringen. Du kan konfigurere trinnene i konfigurationsmenuen på "
"køkkenskærmen."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps  &amp;gt; "
"Industries  &amp;gt; Upgrade your Bar  &amp; Pub package and check the "
"related box"
msgstr ""
"Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu? Du kan stadig nå det. Gå til Apps  "
"&amp;gt; Brancher  &amp;gt; Opgradér din pakke til barer og pubs, og markér "
"det relevante felt"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have two main possibilities in Odoo to ease your replenishment process."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo har du to grundlæggende muligheder for at gøre din "
"genopfyldningsproces nemmere."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Bar package. By doing so, we have installed "
"a bunch of necessary apps to run your bar efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Du har netop installeret Odoo-pakken til barer, og en række nødvendige apps "
"er nu installeret, så du kan drive din bar effektivt."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Med denne pakke i Odoo kan du gennemføre følgende flows for hurtigt at få "
"overblik over de forskellige processer."

